premise_source_doc_sentence: Sawtelle -LSB- sɔːˈtɛl -RSB- is a district in the Westside of the city of Los Angeles , California , partially within the West Los Angeles subregion , that may refer to  (  1  )  a larger district that is part of the city of Los Angeles ,  (  2  )  a smaller unincorporated area of the County of Los Angeles that by definition is not part of the municipality of Los Angeles , or  (  3  )  a combination of these , sometimes known as the Sawtelle area .
